    "steam_appid": 3263230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Sayonara Okaasan》是一首苦乐参半的互动诗，讲述了生命、死亡以及我们在两者之间找到的意义。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作采用原创的手绘艺术和音乐，短小精悍，邀请您进入一个情感四溢的神秘世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感源于制作者亲眼目睹母亲与癌症抗争的经历，这部个人作品通过艺术视觉效果和近似意识流的叙事风格，交织了爱与失落的主题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/57c97db9d77531a78a8a3ceccddee207.webp?t=1733959180\" width=638 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解谜元素引导你通过游戏，跟随文字的线索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘艺术作品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创音乐作品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘且梦幻的叙事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过寻找隐藏物品解锁逃生室风格的额外谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七种语言版本 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sayonara Okaasan》以其细腻而沉郁的艺术风格，引领玩家进入一种深刻的个人情感体验，它不仅仅是一款轻松的游戏，更是艺术家本人对生命脆弱之美的反映。伴随着柔和、阴森的氛围，即使游戏结束，你也可能会思考自己存在的意义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/717e4d4e79ceef210bb162f2dd63e508.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=250 /></span></p>",
